{"tid":1242581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"救護員指控警6.12強拉傷者落白車兼帶走：唔當示威者係人","createTime":"2019-06-19T06:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T08:57:21.000Z","uid":33531,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c08086ab8b96d3d5a4583eff0cfcd7554b088f61","tid":1242581,"uid":33531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:02:36.000Z","msg":"連日來都有發帖反送中惡法，力撐遊行人士及學生的《100毛》老闆之一林日曦，今早在自己facebook發帖，轉載一篇6.12在現場當值的救護員文章，該救護員指控當日有警員強行將傷痕纍纍、呼吸困難的年輕傷者拉落救護車帶走，並拋下一句「唔好阻住我地做野！」文章下款為「心痛的救護員」慨嘆：「脫下制服後，我只是一個普通香港人，我亦希望同所有香港人一樣守護著香港&hellip;香港淪為這個由強權主導的社會，實在感到痛心及無奈！」《蘋果》向消防處查詢事件，正等待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190619/59733276?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR292fKW9DlWp7NKlXFJ0hdNF1x27wvNiuQW5JydgeZATKChFuTL6mdLw8k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190619%2F59733276%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR292fKW9DlWp7NKlXFJ0hdNF1x27wvNiuQW5JydgeZATKChFuTL6mdLw8k&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=0214e420\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190619%2F59733276%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR292fKW9DlWp7NKlXFJ0hdNF1x27wvNiuQW5JydgeZATKChFuTL6mdLw8k&h=19bb4c60\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190619/59733276?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR292fKW9DlWp7NKlXFJ0hdNF1x27wvNiuQW5JydgeZATKChFuTL6mdLw8k</a>"},{"pid":"22b13823035630d1f7e1d236e813d8182283327e","tid":1242581,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":